# Basic Usage

Note that radio buttons are usually used in conjunction with [form
fields](Material-FormField).

    import Material.Radio as Radio

    type Msg
        = Changed

    main =
        Radio.radio
            (Radio.config
                |> Radio.setChecked True
                |> Radio.setOnChange Changed
            )


